<L>__{exterior the pie shop day}
<A>__{fleet street. we see the exterior of mrs. lovett's pie shop. it is tatty and unloved by all. yet it has a strange, ghostly presence to it. imposing and dead at the same time. there is an exterior staircase leading up to a darkened second floor room with a window overlooking the street. the music slows and continues as we see todd, standing in front of the shop, considering it deeply. the general we saw before passes, glancing at todd. here and then gone. todd finally strides to the shop and enters...}
